This directory describes the AST transformation and code generation
for arithmetic expressions. Target architecture is a simple stack machine.

The files:
	expr.scan	The scanner specification
	expr.pars	The parser specification
	expr.ast	The AST specification
	stack.puma	The code generator (stub)
	simplify.puma	The AST transformator (stub)
	main.c		The C-main program
	code		The executable to be produced
	test*.prog	Test cases
	Makefile
	README

	stack-solution.puma
	simplify-solution.puma

Exercises:
	- complete the code generator     (stack.puma)
	- complete the AST transformation (simplify.puma)